snippet.title: Hollowed Trailer
snippet.description:
Hollowed is a 3D side-scrolling platformer where the player controls two different characters at the same time.

Leave a like or subscribe if you enjoyed the vid! Thanks for the support. 

The Florida Interactive Entertainment Academy, or FIEA, is a graduate game-design school at the University of Central Florida. Work on the latest game engines and be mentored by faculty with decades of game-making experience. In 16 months, you can earn a Master’s degree in Interactive Entertainment. 

Ranked #1 by the Princeton Review and ranked Top 5 in 2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, & 2015.
